parameters: I can't afford to lose anymore...

I absolutely must defeat this man.

"Hey! You bastards~! Kick these punks out~!!!"

Flora and her companions have defeated the bandit leader\N[38]!

"It's Ork-san from the recovery service. I secretly contacted him
before coming here."

free...?"
"What the hell?! What does that mean?!!!"
"Honestly, scum like you make me sick~ Buhii~"

"What?! No way! I'd rather die than that...!!!"
The man intends to bite his tongue and die.
Ork-san stuffed his own underwear into the man's mouth.
After this, he'll likely never show his face in public again.
"For now... I feel refreshed. Thank you, Flora."
